title: Bobby Calls His Ex-Girlfriend Lindsay Ell To Talk About Break-Up Song + Lunchbox’s Baby Says First Word + Amy Compliments Someone’s Shoes in Bathroom Stall
itunes:title: Bobby Calls His Ex-Girlfriend Lindsay Ell To Talk About Break-Up Song + Lunchbox’s Baby Says First Word + Amy Compliments Someone’s Shoes in Bathroom Stall
description:
Bobby was talking about how him and his ex-girlfriend are ‘cordial’. So she calls in to talk about a song she may or may not release about their breakup. Lunchbox brings in audio of Baby Box and we decided whether or not he says his first word. We play “Weird or Nah” on Amy complimenting someone’s shoes in the bathroom.
